# Pre-built cross-platform binaries (e.g. macOS arm64 from GitHub Actions CI).
# These are committed by CI workflows so Windows/Linux developers can build
# complete multi-platform packages without requiring a macOS machine.
#
# Files placed here by CI:
#   credential-process-macos-arm64   (from .github/workflows/build-macos.yml)
#   otel-helper-macos-arm64          (from .github/workflows/build-macos.yml)
#
# The 'ccwb package' command automatically includes any files found here
# in the output package alongside locally-built platform binaries.
